She is well known

44
00:04:51,598 --> 00:04:55,762
because she sliced off
her man's sexual organ.

45
00:04:56,937 --> 00:05:03,433
But of course, her life cannot be told
only through that episode."

46
00:05:05,445 --> 00:05:09,643
