1195
02:01:22,160 --> 02:01:23,092
Meaning?

1196
02:01:23,261 --> 02:01:26,890
The man and woman fit each other.

1197
02:01:27,499 --> 02:01:33,199
"Their plus and minus
satisfied each other

1198
02:01:34,005 --> 02:01:36,872
